---
import Base from '../../../layouts/Base.astro';
import Nav from '../../../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Base
  lang="en"
  title="Glimt — Hold on to each other | DYNNI"
  description="Glimt is a calm, private alternative to Snapchat. Share glimt that disappear, gather your closest around a weekly bål. End-to-end encrypted, no ads, no algorithm."
  canonical="https://dynni.no/en/glimt"
  ogTitle="Glimt — Hold on to each other"
  ogDescription="A calm, private alternative to Snapchat. Glimt that disappear, a weekly bål, end-to-end encrypted."
  bodyClass="glimt-page"
  themeColor="#0B1117"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <link rel="alternate" hreflang="nn" href="https://dynni.no/glimt" />
    <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://dynni.no/en/glimt" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/glimt.css" />
    <script src="/js/glimt.js" is:inline></script>
    <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={JSON.stringify({
      '@context': 'https://schema.org',
      '@type': 'SoftwareApplication',
      name: 'Glimt',
      operatingSystem: 'iOS, Android',
      applicationCategory: 'SocialNetworkingApplication',
      description: 'A calm, private alternative to Snapchat. Glimt that disappear, a weekly bål, end-to-end encrypted.',
      author: { '@type': 'Person', name: 'Pål Omland Eilevstjønn', alternateName: 'DYNNI' },
      offers: { '@type': 'Offer', price: '0', priceCurrency: 'NOK' },
    })} />
  </Fragment>

  <canvas class="aurora-canvas" aria-hidden="true"></canvas>
  <div class="grain-layer" aria-hidden="true"></div>
  <div class="vignette" aria-hidden="true"></div>

  <Nav lang="en">
    <div class="lang-switch" slot="lang-switch"><a href="/glimt">NO</a><a href="/en/glimt" class="active">EN</a></div>
    <div class="lang-switch" slot="lang-switch-mobile"><a href="/glimt">NO</a><a href="/en/glimt" class="active">EN</a></div>
  </Nav>

  <main>
    <section class="glimt-hero">
      <div class="glimt-hero-inner">
        <div class="glimt-hero-copy hero-dawn">
          <div class="glimt-badge"><img src="/assets/img/apps/glimt.png" alt="Glimt" /> Glimt</div>
          <h1><span class="h1-line">Life moves fast.</span><span class="h1-line ice">Hold on to each other.</span></h1>
          <p class="lede">
            Year by year it's easy to drift from the people who matter most. Not on purpose, life just takes over. Glimt is a calm little place to be part of each other's days again.
          </p>
          <form class="waitlist" id="waitlist-form">
            <input type="email" id="waitlist-email" placeholder="Your email" required autocomplete="email" />
            <button type="submit"><span class="label">Join the waitlist</span></button>
          </form>
          <div>
            <p class="waitlist-note" id="waitlist-note">We'll send you an invite when Glimt opens. No spam, promise.</p>
            <div class="store-badges">
              <span class="store-badge soon"><i class="fab fa-apple"></i> App Store · coming soon</span>
              <span class="store-badge soon"><i class="fab fa-google-play"></i> Google Play · coming soon</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="glimt-hero-phone">
          <div class="phone">
            <div class="phone-notch"></div>
            <div class="phone-screen phone-screen--hero"><div class="app-resting" aria-hidden="true"><img class="app-bear-img" src="/assets/img/apps/glimt.png" alt="Glimt" /><span class="app-word">Glimt</span><span class="app-hint">a quiet little glimt is waiting</span></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="glimt-story" data-reveal>
      <p>
        We've never been more «connected», yet never more alone. The feed is full of strangers, while the people closest to you get lost in the noise. Glimt flips it: <span class="ice">no algorithm, no feed, no strangers.</span> Just the friends you actually chose, and little moments that vanish the moment they're seen.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="glimt-features">
      <article class="feature reveal-up" data-reveal>
        <div class="feature-text">
          <span class="feature-kicker">Glimt</span>
          <h2>Moments that disappear</h2>
          <p>Share a little glimt from your day. It shows once, then it's gone. No feed to scroll, no likes to chase, no pressure to perform.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-phone">
          <div class="phone phone--sm"><div class="phone-notch"></div><div class="phone-screen"><span class="phone-placeholder">a glimt, soon</span><span class="frost-wipe" aria-hidden="true"></span></div></div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="feature feature--reverse reveal-up" data-reveal>
        <div class="feature-text">
          <span class="feature-kicker">Bål</span>
          <h2>Gather your closest around the fire</h2>
          <p>Once a week you share a little vekeglimt with your closest people. A calm ritual, so you stay part of each other's weeks, not just each other's memories.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-phone">
          <div class="phone phone--sm"><div class="phone-notch"></div><div class="phone-screen"><div class="campfire" aria-hidden="true"><span class="fire-glow"></span><span class="flame outer"></span><span class="flame inner"></span><span class="logs"></span></div><span class="ember-ring" aria-hidden="true"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></div></div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="feature reveal-up" data-reveal>
        <div class="feature-text">
          <span class="feature-kicker">Private</span>
          <h2>End-to-end encrypted. For real.</h2>
          <p>Every glimt is encrypted on your phone before it's sent. Only your friend can open it, not us, not anyone else. What we store is unreadable to us.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-phone">
          <div class="phone phone--sm"><div class="phone-notch"></div><div class="phone-screen"><span class="lock-loop" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fa-solid fa-lock-open lock-open"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-lock lock-closed"></i></span></div></div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="glimt-values">
      <h2>Built for you, not for advertisers</h2>
      <ul class="values-grid" data-reveal>
        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-eye-slash"></i><h3>No tracking</h3><p>We don't track you across apps or the web. Ever.</p></li>
        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-ban"></i><h3>No ads</h3><p>No ads, no algorithm deciding what you see.</p></li>
        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-lock"></i><h3>End-to-end</h3><p>Your content is encrypted. We can't read it.</p></li>
        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-earth-europe"></i><h3>European</h3><p>Built in Norway, GDPR at the core, we never sell your data.</p></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="glimt-cta">
      <h2>Join from the start</h2>
      <p>We open Glimt to a few at a time. Sign up to be among the first.</p>
      <form class="waitlist" id="waitlist-form-2">
        <input type="email" id="waitlist-email-2" placeholder="Your email" required autocomplete="email" />
        <button type="submit"><span class="label">Join the waitlist</span></button>
      </form>
      <p class="waitlist-note" id="waitlist-note-2"></p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer lang="en">
    <p class="glimt-footer-links" slot="default">
      <a href="/en/glimt/privacy">Privacy</a> ·
      <a href="/en/glimt/terms">Terms</a> ·
      <a href="/en/glimt/child-safety">Child safety</a> ·
      <a href="/en/glimt/delete-account">Delete account</a>
    </p>
  </Footer>

  <script is:inline>
    (function () {
      var SUPABASE_URL = 'https://khhjqjtmhybwfrkhttoa.supabase.co';
      var SUPABASE_ANON = 'eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJpc3MiOiJzdXBhYmFzZSIsInJlZiI6ImtoaGpxanRtaHlid2Zya2h0dG9hIiwicm9sZSI6ImFub24iLCJpYXQiOjE3ODE5NDA4NjYsImV4cCI6MjA5NzUxNjg2Nn0.Xu1UKzzJzg2dO-4BdENCpVNQ4jJFUw9Iz4qOLb1NMCQ';
      function join(email) {
        return fetch(SUPABASE_URL + '/rest/v1/waitlist', {
          method: 'POST',
          headers: { 'apikey': SUPABASE_ANON, 'Authorization': 'Bearer ' + SUPABASE_ANON, 'Content-Type': 'application/json', 'Prefer': 'return=minimal' },
          body: JSON.stringify({ email: email })
        });
      }
      function wire(formId, noteId) {
        var form = document.getElementById(formId);
        if (!form) return;
        var note = document.getElementById(noteId);
        form.addEventListener('submit', function (e) {
          e.preventDefault();
          var input = form.querySelector('input[type="email"]');
          var email = (input.value || '').trim();
          if (!email) return;
          form.classList.add('busy');
          join(email).then(function (res) {
            form.classList.remove('busy');
            if (res.ok) { form.classList.add('done'); if (note) note.textContent = "Thanks! You're on the list. We'll let you know when Glimt opens. 🐻‍❄️"; input.value = ''; }
            else if (res.status === 409) { if (note) note.textContent = "You're already on the list. Thanks! 🐻‍❄️"; }
            else { if (note) note.textContent = 'Something went wrong. Try again, or email paal@dynni.no.'; }
          }).catch(function () { form.classList.remove('busy'); if (note) note.textContent = 'Something went wrong. Try again, or email paal@dynni.no.'; });
        });
      }
      wire('waitlist-form', 'waitlist-note');
      wire('waitlist-form-2', 'waitlist-note-2');
    })();
  </script>
</Base>
